<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/main.css">
    <script src="/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <%-include('header.ejs') %>
    <div class="main-page">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-md-center">      
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-5 mx-1 my-3 p-3 bg-body rounded shadow">
                    <h6 class="border-bottom pb-2 mb-0">알림판</h6>
                    <div class="d-flex text-body-secondary pt-3">
                        <div class="pb-3 mb-0 small lh-sm border-bottom w-100">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                                <strong class="text-gray-text-light position-relative">총 <%- totalCount %>개 법인 &nbsp;
                                    <span class="position-absolute top-0 start-100 translate-middle badge rounded-pill bg-danger"><%- countTermEnd %></span>
                                </strong>
                                <a href="/profile">확인하기</a>
                            </div>
                        <span class="d-block"><%- countTermEnd %>개 법인이 안내가 필요합니다.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex text-body-secondary pt-3">
                        <div class="pb-3 mb-0 small lh-sm border-bottom w-100">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                                <strong class="text-gray-dark">신규등록</strong>
                                <a href="/register">등록하기</a>
                            </div>
                            <span class="d-block">신규 법인 정보를 등록할 수 있습니다.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-5 mx-1 my-3 p-3 bg-body rounded shadow">
                    <h6 class="border-bottom pb-2 mb-0">최근 등록 법인</h6>
                    <div class="d-flex text-body-secondary pt-3">
                        <div class="pb-3 mb-0 small lh-sm border-bottom w-100">
                            <% if(lists[0]){ %>
                            <span class="d-block"><a href="/detail/<%=(lists[0].id)%>"><%=(lists[0].corp)%></a></span>
                            <% }%>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex text-body-secondary pt-3">
                        <div class="pb-3 mb-0 small lh-sm border-bottom w-100">
                            <% if(lists[1]){ %>
                            <span class="d-block"><a href="/detail/<%=(lists[1].id)%>"><%=(lists[1].corp)%></a></span>
                            <% }%>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex text-body-secondary pt-3">
                        <div class="pb-3 mb-0 small lh-sm border-bottom w-100">
                            <% if(lists[2]){ %>
                            <span class="d-block"><a href="/detail/<%=(lists[2].id)%>"><%=(lists[2].corp)%></a></span>
                            <% }%>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-10 mx-1 my-3 p-3 bg-body rounded shadow">
                    <h6 class="border-bottom pb-2 mb-0">회원 관리</h6>
                    <div class="d-flex text-body-secondary pt-3">
                        <div class="pb-3 mb-0 small lh-sm border-bottom w-100">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                                <strong class="text-gray-text-light position-relative">총 <%- totalUser %>명의 회원 &nbsp;
                                    <span class="position-absolute top-0 start-100 translate-middle badge rounded-pill bg-danger"><%- newUser %></span>
                                </strong>
                                <a href="/user">확인하기</a>
                            </div>
                        <span class="d-block"><%- newUser %>명의 회원이 가입승인을 기다리고 있습니다!</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="container marketing pt-4 mt-5">
                <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto text-center"> 
                    <h4>회사 별 직원 정보&임원 임기관리 사이트 입니다.</h4>
                    <h4>회원가입 후, 관리자의 승인이 완료되면<br>다음 업무를 할 수 있습니다.</h4>
                </div>
                <h3 class="p-2 mx-5 border-bottom">가능 업무</h3>
                <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
                <div class="row px-5">
                  <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100" height="100" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-card-checklist p-3" viewBox="0 0 16 16"> <path d="M14.5 3a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v9a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-13a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-9a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5zm-13-1A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0 3.5v9A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 14h13a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5v-9A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 14.5 2z"/> <path d="M7 5.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h5a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-5a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5m-1.496-.854a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-1.5 1.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-.5-.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708l.146.147 1.146-1.147a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0M7 9.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h5a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-5a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5m-1.496-.854a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-1.5 1.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-.5-.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .708-.708l.146.147 1.146-1.147a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0"/> </svg>
                    <h4 class="fw-normal">1. 회사 관리</h2>
                    <p>'회사' 페이지에서 회사 정보 확인 및 수정이 가능합니다.</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100" height="100" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-pencil-square p-3" viewBox="0 0 16 16"> <path d="M15.502 1.94a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .706L14.459 3.69l-2-2L13.502.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .707 0l1.293 1.293zm-1.75 2.456-2-2L4.939 9.21a.5.5 0 0 0-.121.196l-.805 2.414a.25.25 0 0 0 .316.316l2.414-.805a.5.5 0 0 0 .196-.12l6.813-6.814z"/> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M1 13.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 2.5 15h11a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5v-6a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0v6a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-11a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-11a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5H9a.5.5 0 0 0 0-1H2.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1 2.5z"/> </svg>
                    <h4 class="fw-normal">2. 회사 입력</h2>
                    <p>'등록' 페이지에서 회사 정보 입력이 가능합니다.</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100" height="100" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-whatsapp p-3" viewBox="0 0 16 16"> <path d="M13.601 2.326A7.85 7.85 0 0 0 7.994 0C3.627 0 .068 3.558.064 7.926c0 1.399.366 2.76 1.057 3.965L0 16l4.204-1.102a7.9 7.9 0 0 0 3.79.965h.004c4.368 0 7.926-3.558 7.93-7.93A7.9 7.9 0 0 0 13.6 2.326zM7.994 14.521a6.6 6.6 0 0 1-3.356-.92l-.24-.144-2.494.654.666-2.433-.156-.251a6.56 6.56 0 0 1-1.007-3.505c0-3.626 2.957-6.584 6.591-6.584a6.56 6.56 0 0 1 4.66 1.931 6.56 6.56 0 0 1 1.928 4.66c-.004 3.639-2.961 6.592-6.592 6.592m3.615-4.934c-.197-.099-1.17-.578-1.353-.646-.182-.065-.315-.099-.445.099-.133.197-.513.646-.627.775-.114.133-.232.148-.43.05-.197-.1-.836-.308-1.592-.985-.59-.525-.985-1.175-1.103-1.372-.114-.198-.011-.304.088-.403.087-.088.197-.232.296-.346.1-.114.133-.198.198-.33.065-.134.034-.248-.015-.347-.05-.099-.445-1.076-.612-1.47-.16-.389-.323-.335-.445-.34-.114-.007-.247-.007-.38-.007a.73.73 0 0 0-.529.247c-.182.198-.691.677-.691 1.654s.71 1.916.81 2.049c.098.133 1.394 2.132 3.383 2.992.47.205.84.326 1.129.418.475.152.904.129 1.246.08.38-.058 1.171-.48 1.338-.943.164-.464.164-.86.114-.943-.049-.084-.182-.133-.38-.232"/> </svg>
                    <h4 class="fw-normal">3. 회사 별 알림</h2>
                    <p>'회사' 페이지의 회사 상호를 클릭해 회사 '상세 페이지'에서 상담 기록과 카카오톡 안내가 가능합니다.</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100" height="100" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-person-circle p-3" viewBox="0 0 16 16"> <path d="M11 6a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0"/> <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M0 8a8 8 0 1 1 16 0A8 8 0 0 1 0 8m8-7a7 7 0 0 0-5.468 11.37C3.242 11.226 4.805 10 8 10s4.757 1.225 5.468 2.37A7 7 0 0 0 8 1"/> </svg>
                    <h4 class="fw-normal">4. 나의 정보관리</h2>
                    <p>'나의 정보' 페이지에서 나의 정보 변경이 가능합니다.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%-include('footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>